<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <%= render "layouts/head" %>
<body id="splash">
  <div id="wrapper">
    <header>
      <h1>
        <div id="logo">Vaisala</div>
        <span>/ RoadDSS Value Calculator</span>
      </h1>
      <div id="road"></div>
      <div id="contact"><%= link_to "Contact Vaisala", contact_path %></div>
    </header>
    <section>
      <h2>Calculate potential winter road maintenance savings</h2>
      <div><p>The Vaisala RoadDSS Value Calculator helps users determine the potential savings and benefits of using the Vaisala RoadDSS Decision Support System software for Winter Road Maintenance. The calculator uses a small number of input items from the user, generates a few assumed values,  and produces a detailed list of savings that include labor, materials, maintenance and wear, and increased revenue.</p></div>
      <div><p>
        <a class="scroller" href="#new_record">Begin Calculations</a>
        <span>Provide basic information to begin calculating savings.</span>
      </p></div>
    </section>
    <section>
      <p id="link-out">Find out more about <a href="http://www.vaisala.com/en/roads/applications/Pages/default.aspx">RoadDSS</a></p>
      <ul id="screenshots">
        <li><a class="screenshot" href="<%= image_path("screenshot-1.png") %>" target="_blank"><%= image_tag "screenshot-1.png" %></a></li>
        <li><a class="screenshot" href="<%= image_path("screenshot-2.png") %>" target="_blank"><%= image_tag "screenshot-2.png" %></a></li>
        <li><a class="screenshot" href="<%= image_path("screenshot-3.png") %>" target="_blank"><%= image_tag "screenshot-3.png" %></a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <div class="easy-clear">
      <%= yield %>
      <div class="sidebar">
        <h3><span>RoadDSS Benefits</span></h3>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Efficiency
            <blockquote>Calculate monetary and time savings due to increased efficiency for Road Operations Maintenance groups, including driving, de-icing materials, cleanup, vehicle maintenance, fuel consumption, and IT reduced costs.</blockquote>
          </li>
          <li>
            Publicity
            <blockquote>Calculate publicity related reductions in complaint and litigation costs.</blockquote>
          </li>
          <li>
            Safety
            <blockquote>Assess savings increases in safety and mobility, and pollution reduction costs that benefit the entire community.</blockquote>
          </li>
          <li>
            Additional Benefits
            <blockquote>Provide a list of additional benefits such as reporting, planning, performance tracking, streamlined operations, transparency, marketing and community safety.</blockquote>
          </li>
          <li>
            Assumptions Editing
            <blockquote>Allow customers to change assumptions to get a more accurate idea of the potential savings for both the software users and the community in general.</blockquote>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

